
The authors suggested and tested an zzso to select optimal placement of stationary and mobile points for controlling ambient air quality on borderline of united zzso protective zone of industrial zzso The method involves zzso analysis to outline sites even in levels and lists of zzso on borderline of united zzso protective zone of industrial zzso zzso value of the occupational control parameters is evaluated through zzso analysis of general level of surface concentration of zzso and zzso contribution into zzso For each enterprise, separate control program is zzso Tests of the method demonstrated that it is effective and conclusive in formation of minimally sufficient programs for occupational control in complicated conditions of industrial centers with zzso enterprises, when industrial releases are close in composition and in created pollution zzso 

